article_id:1595,category_name:Events,title_name:A Raid Event Revival, Fractured Futures, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/6eb73526efffc4661a3ffee280d81cf0.png,message:<div>The Fractured Futures raid event revival will begin <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1600668000"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>During this event, you can use co-op play to fight against the light-attuned raid boss.</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/6eb73526efffc4661a3ffee280d81cf0.png"></div><div>On one fateful day, a loved one was lost, and a possible future was stolen forever... While lamenting over memories of days gone by, the prince is approached by a dragon named Chronos. The dragon offers to use his powers to alter time, giving the prince a chance to set things right&mdash;no matter the consequences!<br><br>Notes:<br>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate in event quests.<br>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to play co-op.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<br><br></div>,start_time:1600408800,update_time1600394935